# Node.js Backend Toolkit 🚀

Production-ready backend utilities for building scalable Node.js applications.

## Features
- JWT Authentication Middleware
- Paystack Payment Integration
- Email Service (Nodemailer)
- PDF Invoice Generator
- Rate Limiting
- MongoDB Connection Setup

## Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/nodejs-backend-toolkit
cd nodejs-backend-toolkit
npm install